Body:
with expected_protocol(ik.yokogawa.Yokogawa6370, [':FORMat:DATA REAL,64',
    ':INIT:SMOD 1', ':INIT:SMOD 2', ':INIT:SMOD 3', ':INIT:SMOD?',
    ':INIT:SMOD?', ':INIT:SMOD?'], ['1', '2', '3']) as inst:
    for mode in inst.SweepModes:
        inst.sweep_mode = mode
    for mode in inst.SweepModes:
        assert inst.sweep_mode == mode
